title: If I Could Only Remember My Name - David Crosby
description:
IF I COULD ONLY REMEMBER MY NAME
David Crosby

Released 1971

Remastered for CD in 2006

Ripped from 2006 HDCD remaster to FLAC.

Presently (11/2014) the only CD to FLAC torrent of this album on Pirate Bay.

No bonus tracks, no 5.1 DVD Audio - just the original track list, but ripped from the excellent remaster. This album has never sounded so good.

TRACK LIST

01 Music Is Love
02 Cowboy Movie
03 Tamalpais High (At About 3)
04 Laughing
05 What Are Their Names?
06 Traction in the Rain
07 Song with No Words (Tree with No Leaves)
08 Orleans
09 I'd Swear There Was Somebody Here
